text: Make an appointment to see your new home! This charming 2-bedroom residence is packed with features: all appliances included, a newly updated kitchen with beautiful cabinets and countertops, and a spacious utility room. Enjoy stunning Mount Baker views from your 1/3-acre leveled and cleared lot, perfect for building your dream shop. The great-sized carport offers ample storage. Just minutes from downtown Concrete and the Skagit River, youll have easy access to shopping, dining, and recreation. This property is also a fantastic investment opportunity, ideal for short-term rentals with breathtaking mountain views or long-term tenants. Dont miss out!

Welcome to this meticulously maintained rambler, boasting 4 beds and 2.5 baths, enjoy the open floor plan that seamlessly connects the gorgeous kitchen to large family room. The large primary bedroom features a walk-in closet and an oversized soaking tub. Entertain effortlessly on the huge deck, overlooking beautifully landscaped grounds. This home features a spacious 2-car garage with an additional 12x36 attached garage including a 240V outlet. Additional perks include AC, central vac, generator/Electric car outlet, invisible pet fence, and a sprinkler system. Recent upgrades include a new roof and fresh paint. Relax in the hot tub and embrace the epitome of comfort and style in this remarkable property.

Premium building going on in this gated community close to Rasar State Park. Gorgeous one acre lot with southern exposure mountain views and no height restrictions. Neighbor to the left owns 10 acres for a super private feel. Short distance to the town of Sedro Wooley and Burlington. Paved streets with underground power plus underground conduit installed for cable TV, phone, & high speed internet. Street lights installed. Marketable timber on lot. Well and septic needed but can be done. Rasar Park is known for miles of walking trails, bird watching, fishing and the Skagit River. This is the last lot available in the Forest Park Estates at this time. Newly built homes are selling just under $670k. Great investment or personal property.

Enjoy the convenience of this main level condo. Home includes 2 good size bedrooms, kitchen with granite counters and an eating island, hardwood floors and 1 3/4 baths. Sit and enjoy your covered private balcony while not having to think about exterior maintenance or landscaping. Head down the hill to all the local amenities or enjoy Whistle Lake and the Anacortes Forest Lands within a couple blocks of your door. Home includes 1 covered parking space and storage unit. Plenty of additional guest parking as well. Price reduced for a quick sale. Please bring offers.

text: Discover the appeal of the highly sought after Skagit Highlands neighborhood! Near the eastern edge of Mt Vernon only a 3.5 mile straight shot to I-5 for easy access to all points N and S. Shopping, schools, medical, parks, recreation all within easy reach even tho this neighborhood is out of mainstream with no thru traffic, etc.. Head east and your minutes from Big Lake, Overlook golf and beautiful rural Skagit County. This 2110 sf 3 bd 2.5 bath is one of the best values on the market today. Its well cared for, has open floor plan, large primary w/ walkin closet and ensuite, granite counters and ample storage. Awesome backyard, fenced for privacy with a nice covered patio area and backs up to lush green space. Makes you want to get home!

Come enjoy the peace and quiet. A private well was put in just before the moratorium. River access on the road across from the property for you to enjoy all the river has to offer. Bring your vision and build your dream home.

Serene 1 acre lot near Little Mountain, located just in the SE corner of Mount Vernon. Only 2 Minutes from I-5 yet down a private street that makes for a very peaceful quiet location. Located only 30min in-between Bellingham and Everett. This is a rare lot with incredible opportunity. Flat area for a building footprint w/plenty of room plus enjoy privacy with the lay of the land between the neighbors. Wetlands study has been completed not located on lot, approved 3 bedroom septic design. electric & water street accessible. Propane will be required for gas. Bring your builder to envision you next home.

Upscale mountain view, open floor plan home with designer touches on a gorgeous 1 acre lot. Rich luxury vinyl plank flooring and hydronic floor heating throughout with HP mini splits for heat and A/C. Gorgeous show kitchen with oversized island, six burner range and commercial grade hood, tile backsplash, plus tons of workspace and storage. Living room with vaulted ceiling, oversized horizontal stone surround gas fireplace, and plenty of windows to enjoy the natural light and mountain views. Large primary bedroom looks out to the wooded greenspace and features a spacious bath with tile backsplash and walk in shower. Private, expansive covered back porch for year 'round enjoyment and a large yard with custom fire pit. Wired for generator.

This beautifully updated 2-bedroom home with an office offers breathtaking water views of Fidalgo Bay and stunning vistas of Mount Baker. The primary bathroom boasts luxurious heated floors, perfect for those chilly mornings. Recent upgrades include new windows and electrical ensuring peace of mind and modern convenience. The downstairs daylight basement is wired for a kitchen, presenting a fantastic opportunity for a mother-in-law suite with its own entrance. Dont miss out on this gem, where comfort meets potential in one of the most scenic spots in Washington!

text: Enjoy prime in-town living and unmatched water views of Fidalgo Bay, Cap Sante Marina, and downtown Anacortes! This remarkable home features a 1, 000 sq ft deck for indoor-outdoor living, panoramic windows, vaulted ceilings, on a dead end road. The beautiful ensuite boasts exquisite finishes, creating a spa-like sanctuary and the primary closet includes a washer/dryer for convenient single-story living. Downstairs, you'll find a secondary kitchenette and a covered patio for year-round entertainment. The oversized lot offers space for a potential shop or ADU. Don't miss the large workshop with backyard access, perfect for any hobby or project! Truly rare to find a fully renovated home, located in town, with water views, on a large lot!

text: OUTSTANDING rambler built by Presidio Construction, known as Dream Home 2000, which boasts stunning craftsmanship & pride of ownership. Stamped concrete circular driveway leads to portico w/ captivating beveled glass front doors. Open concept living room w/ cozy fireplace, upscale carpeting & granite tile. Updated Chefs Kitchen w/ stainless steel appliances, Wood-Mode innovative storage, granite counters & tiled backsplash. Primary bedroom w/ floor to ceiling custom cabinetry, fireplace & private deck access to hot tub. Luxurious Spa-like bathroom w/ beautiful granite, double sinks, vanity, glass block shower & walk-in closet w/ closet carousel. Move-in-ready theater room. 2 additional bedrooms that adjoin full bath. 3+ pull-thru garage.

Come check out this cute, affordable home of yesteryear. Downstairs you will find kitchen, dining room, living room, a good size primary bedroom plus 1 full bath & 1 half bath. Check out the handy pass thru area from the kitchen to the good sized living room with gas piped in the fireplace for easy cozy evenings. Adorable arched doorway from the dining room to the living room & some glass doorknobs too. Upstairs you find another large bedroom, loads of closets in the ample landing for toys, computers, printers etc. Also a separate room upstairs could be a den, sewing room, hobby area or add a door & closet & have a 3rd bedroom. Private yard, patio with brick fireplace plus a large 2 car garage with storage above. Room for an RV or boat too!

Discover the charm of this Craftsman-style home nestled on a spacious corner lot. Step onto the enclosed front porch and into a living room adorned with window seats, wainscoting, and gleaming fir softwood floors. The kitchen beckons with stainless steel appliances and a cozy eat-in cove. Retreat to the bathroom featuring a classic claw foot tub. From your backyard, soak in breathtaking views of Fidalgo Bay and Mt. Baker. Entertain under the pergola patio or let loved ones play freely in the fully fenced yard. Benefit from ample storage space below the home. With schools, restaurants, and shopping just a short stroll away, this residence offers unmatched convenience and character. Don't let this opportunity slip by!

Escape to tranquility in this private, secluded home nestled on just over an acre in a beautiful hillside neighborhood of custom-built homes. Ideally located between Seattle and Vancouver, and near Fidalgo and Whidbey Islands, it offers stunning Skagit Valley views. Vaulted ceilings and expansive picture windows flood the interior with natural light, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. Gourmet kitchen with a huge island that's perfect for entertaining. The lower level, recently utilized as an Airbnb, serves perfectly as guest quarters or a MIL suite. Outside, enjoy a deck and patio surrounded by mature landscaping and fully fenced backyard with access to Little Mountain hiking trails, enhancing the allure of this serene retreat.

This recently painted 2 bedroom home is situated in a private setting in a 55+ community. There is a storage shed for extra storage. Spacious Living/Dining area. Relax in your beautiful spacious walk-in shower just off your large Master Bedroom. Dogs and Cats are allowed - check with Park for specific restrictions.

Step into this beautifully updated and well-maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with an ideal floorplan for relaxation and entertaining. Featuring a newly painted interior, a newer roof, and modern upgrades throughout, this residence blends style and comfort. The primary suite is a standout with French doors opening to a charming outdoor space. Enjoy a spacious, well-kept yard perfect for activities and gardening. Conveniently located close to town, youll have easy access to shops, schools, and parks. Dont miss out on this move-in-ready gem with all the modern touches!

Welcome to this diamond in the rough waiting for your personal touch. Centrally located, this property is conveniently close to schools, hospitals, and shopping. This home offers a fantastic opportunity for those w/ a vision. While it needs a lot of TLC, the potential is limitless. Imagine transforming this space into your dream home, with ample room for customization & upgrades. The large yard is perfect for outdoor activities & gardening. With a bit of creativity and effort this property can truly shine.Dont miss out on this incredible fixer-upper opportunity. Whether youre an investor looking for your next project or a homeowner ready to create a personalized haven, this home is a blank canvas waiting for your inspiration.

Classic updated mid century modern home! Unbelievable soaring vaulted living room ceiling, featuring a grand stone fireplace. With retaining the original features, there is new carpet, tile floors and light fixtures throughout. The large kitchen radiates lots of light, preserved cabinetry, new counters, sink, stove top, eating bar...and dining area. Huge oversized primary is en-suite w/remodeled bath, new tiled tub surround, counters and walk-in closet. Two nice sized bedrooms/remodeled guest bath. Wall of windows w/slider to patio and hot tub. Lets walk outside...entertain out back in the 14x16 gazebo surrounded by cedars, ferns, trails to the pond and cute little bridge! Just relax and meditate in the glam shed! Its magical! Fenced yard!

Versatile multi-level home with custom touches throughout! Gorgeous main level living space features a cozy gas stove. The impeccable kitchen includes custom hickory cabinets, granite counters, black stainless appliances, and a dual fuel stove/range. Main level also offers a full bath and bedroom. The upper level has a spacious primary bedroom and bathroom. The lower level includes a bar area (future kitchen potential), space near the laundry room for storage (with future bathroom potential), bonus living room, and the 3rd bedroom. The newer detached shop is wired for water, sewer, natural gas, and EV charging. Expansive driveway for RV and vehicle parking. Large fully fenced backyard and a front yard with large flowering cherry trees.

This charming 1, 765 square-foot Craftsman-style home, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, is situated on just over a quarter-acre and is ready for new owners to call home. It includes two spacious living rooms, large windows that fill the space with natural light, and a cozy wood-burning fireplace for chilly days. The expansive master suite boasts a luxurious en-suite with a soaking tub and a walk-in closet. A small room at the top of the stairs is perfect for a den, craft room or nursery. The property also offers a two-car garage, large fully fenced private backyard with a massive deck, pond, and a storage shed. Beautiful custom sliding back door offers a pet door for the fur babies to have easy access to back yard.

First time on the market in 54 years, this lovingly custom-built, immaculately maintained Westside Mount Vernon home is ready for new beginnings! Sitting on one beautifully landscaped acre in a peaceful neighborhood, a large, bright living room greets you upon entering the home, then flows nicely into the adjacent dining room. The tidy kitchen has a eating space & view of the great backyard. Also on the main floor are one bedroom, currently used as an office, a half bath, utility room & family room w/slider to the back patio. Upstairs are three bedrooms, a full bath, & a three-quarter bath off the primary bedroom. Note the three closets in the primary bedroom! Ample extra storage area at the top of the stairs and extra closets throughout.

Step inside to discover a freshly new interior paint throughout the house and new carpet upstairs. The spacious living area is enhanced by laminated vinyl flooring, creating a modern yet cozy atmosphere. The kitchen is a standout feature with stainless steel appliances that complement the clean, contemporary design. It's perfect for culinary enthusiasts and those who appreciate a well-appointed space for cooking and dining. Don't miss the opportunity to own this gem at 1505 E Division St, where modern updates meet a serene location with unparalleled views. Schedule your tour today and envision yourself enjoying the best of what this home has to offer.

Welcome to this mid-century home that offers many possibilities to the right buyer! The main level features a nice kitchen, dining and living room w/gas fireplace. On a clear day, enjoy a great view across the valley to the Olympic mountains. Two bedrooms, a full bath and a laundry area round out the main floor, which has wood floors and built-ins throughout. The lower level features many possibilities with another complete living areafull kitchen, comfortable family room w/ gas fireplace, bedroom, bonus room and a full bathroom. Outside is a private backyard with a spacious deck and a covered seating area. New roof installed 2023. The alley-accessed garage and great location near hospital and downtown make this an ideal investment.

Well maintained Lake Cavanaugh property with 3 buildings. Main house of 3066 sqft has upper-level suite w/office space, main level has kitchen, dining room, living room w/large wall of windows, fireplace, den/office/bedroom, fully finished rec-room that can be used as extra bedroom. The property features oversized 3-car garage that has a 480 sqft studio on top floor and it also connected to the main house 2nd floor deck. A tall garage-bay is ready for your car-lift or additional storage area. The cute beach front cabin has 2 bunk rooms, living room & kitchen area (no water hooked up) & deck overlooking the lake. The 60 beach front has patio, fire pit, dock & boat lift. Summer is here and the potential fun for this home is endless!

{Riverside Opportunity Awaits You!}Whether you are looking for your own riverside park setting or a potential income source, this shy 12 acres along the stilly offers incredible opportunity. Riverside property includes 20 dry camp sites w/portable bathrooms, picnic tables & beautiful natural surroundings; a 2 bedroom, 1 bath open concept home w/lpv flooring; a shop or ADU studio style unit; & 6 RV sites-3 w/full hook ups & 3 w/water only. Home has a new roof being installed prior to close. Plenty of garden space, fishing opportunity, BBQing w/bon fires or just sheer relaxation floating in the river; this place is a must see! Buyer to verify all information to include regulations regarding camping/RV/ADU rental opportunities.
